comments: Brown (BOS) and Lowry (MIA) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Brown (BOS) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds and MIA retains possession.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in Brown's (BOS) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Adebayo (MIA) is already in Brown's (BOS) path as he sets the pick and is firming up when contact occurs.
Oladipo (MIA) makes incidental contact with Tatum (BOS) during the rebound.
Oladipo (MIA) briefly places an arm to Tatum's (BOS) front defending the drive and marginal contact occurs.
Lowry (MIA) cleanly dislodges the ball from Williams (BOS) and any ensuing contact is incidental.
Williams (BOS) makes marginal body contact with Oladipo (MIA) that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Oladipo (MIA) brushes the ball as Smart (BOS) releases the pass and any further contact is incidental.
Strus (MIA) moves laterally into Brown's (BOS) path during his drive to the basket and marginal contact occurs.
Lowry (MIA) pins the ball to his hip as his gather and takes three steps.
Williams (BOS) makes marginal contact to Lowry (MIA) contesting his driving shot attempt.
Lowry (MIA) places a hand against Tatum's (BOS) back but the contact is marginal as he makes the pass.

Replay review of the foul called on Brown (BOS) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful, as there is no clear and conclusive angle to overturn the call. Brown makes contact with Adebayo (MIA) with his elbow during his shooting motion.
Butler (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in Brown's (BOS) path and does not deliver contact.
Horford (BOS) makes marginal contact with Strus' (MIA) body after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Smart (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in Oladipo's (MIA) path and marginal contact occurs.
Butler (MIA) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Adebayo (MIA) brings his arms forward to contest the shot attempt at the basket and marginal contact occurs with Smart's (BOS) non-shooting arm.
Horford (BOS) legally contests Butler's (MIA) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Adebayo (MIA) commits a take foul on Smart (BOS).
Smart (BOS) makes marginal contact to Strus' (MIA) wrist after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Horford (BOS) makes contact with the ball, but continues forward and makes contact to Oladipo's (MIA) arm that affects his ability to rebound.
Smart (BOS) places a collapsed forearm against Strus' (MIA) side and does not apply force defending his jump shot attempt.
